caption.text:
We’re looking hire a wildly creative & talented scriptwriter. You’ll make a base salary + 5% of monthly revenue because we want you to win big with the company. 

*You must have experience growing brands FAST.*

Please include WRITE OF PASSAGE at the start of your message to be considered. And let us know why you should get the job. 

Who we’re looking for

I’m looking for a full time creative to join my team. 

You’ll be working directly with me (Yasin) in my education businesses, Viral Video Club. 

This is the perfect job for someone that’s already an incredible creative strategist that’s wanting to become a key player in a fast growing business. 

There are opportunities for salary and responsibility growth. I am looking for a right hand person.

Your Role 

- Help VVC grow faster. I’ve grown it to 1,00,000 followers alone. Imagine the speed we can grow and the impact we can have when there are 2 minds working on this!

- Creative Strategist for clients of the company and students of the Bootcamp & Community. Take what we learn from our own social growth and apply these lessons to help our customers grow faster

- Detailed video notes for clients regarding ideation, hooks, structure, scripting, and editing

- Ideation for clients as well as developing outlines for approved video ideas

- Generating monthly reports summarizing key learnings from content published in the month for clients

- Helping Yasin build out course materials and deliver on VVC products

If you want me to send you a doc that makes creating stories like this easy, comment STORY. If we hit 1000 comments, I’ll send it to you for free. 

How to film yourself playing sport (in this case running). Heavily influenced by a beautiful piece from @bryanhynes_

Love running on the track and wanted to find more ways to encorporate the things I love into what I do here. So expect me to shoehorn plenty more sports/mincemeat practises into my content haha!

Please add any suggestions of other sports/forms of movement in the comments and I’ll pick the most upvoted ones?
